Privacy Policy

This application is used internally by Smoky Mountain Studios to generate
invoices and sync them with QuickBooks Online.

The application accesses customer names, invoice line items, pricing,
taxes, and totals solely for the purpose of creating and managing invoices
within QuickBooks Online.

No data is sold, shared, or transferred to third parties.
No data is used for advertising or marketing purposes.
No data is stored outside of the QuickBooks Online platform except
temporarily during invoice generation.

For questions, contact:
